{"tid":2330383,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"到底連登仔有幾多係咁想俾人管?","createTime":"2020-12-18T03:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-21T11:30:59.000Z","uid":61511,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d0d9eacb6bdd1d88830b1c92d86c981fd90803d7","tid":2330383,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T03:40:20.000Z","msg":"以下呢兩個建議BAM 5毛POST一直都有人推,仲推得郁<br />\n<br />\nAdmin 搞搞五毛account啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2289262/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2289262/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n我叫admin搞「！」系統，引黎五毛瘋狂狙撃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2196213/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2196213/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n主調都係用自己既標準去BAM 5毛<br />\n<br />\n但如果USER自己識分又洗乜要用你果套標準BAM?<br />\n<br />\n就話,係為左d唔識分既USER用<br />\n<br />\n咁人地唔識分你就用自己果套標準去apply落人地到 而唔係教人點分既?<br />\n<br />\n仲要無任何理據<br />\n好簡單一個我覺得就當係<br />\n<br />\n正如之前唔同意泛民委任既就俾人話係5毛<br />\n而家呢?結果係點?<br />\n<br />\n由運動初期開始屌泛民就=5毛要拉<br />\n到到而家年半先叫有改善少少 年半喎大佬 <br />\n當你俾人bam完年半先解封,都無癮啦<br />\n<br />\n憑咩用你果套咁既標準去bam 5毛呢?<br />\n<br />\n最後就係<br />\n<br />\n呢套標準 你俾得管理員話事,他朝一日佢唔同意你,可以bam埋<br />\n真心唔明點解仲要一直推呢d post落去"},{"pid":"59096aa68fdc3fc5053d42bf24332951021a5b6a","tid":2330383,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T03:45:34.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"6c1a5da9906765d966804b0af0b571e31ab82667","tid":2330383,"uid":61511,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T04:04:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s